Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.56,0:00:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚要和提安娜一起表演\Nperforming with Tiana tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.82,0:00:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你不如打造一首诋毁他的歌\NWhy don't you spit some napalm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.09,0:00:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,埋葬他\Non a diss track and bury him
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.83,0:00:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,和他在乎的一切\Nand everything he cares about.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.12,0:00:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,艺人监理部没有人有能力能管理这个交易\NThere is no head of A&R to oversee the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.02,0:00:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们雇佣了泽维尔罗森 谁\NWe hired Xavier Rosen. Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.92,0:00:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,考虑到盖哲思女士受到的威胁\NGiven the dangers to Ms. Gathers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.86,0:00:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,法庭允许保释\Nthe court agrees to grant bail.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.36,0:00:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,令我最骄傲的是\NWhat I was most proud of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.69,0:00:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你收买了那个医生钱了\Nwas that you paid off that doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.60,0:00:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,知道自己跟自己父亲如出一辙感觉怎么样\NHow does it feel to know you're just like your daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.13,0:00:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我不得不处理掉几个人 嗯\NI had to put in work on a couple of cats. Mmhmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.27,0:00:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那三个想致我们于死地的人\NThe three horsemen who wanted us dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.87,0:00:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不 还有第四个\NWell, there was a fourth horseman.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.44,0:00:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但肖恩 他不是个告密的人\NBut Shine, he ain't no snitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.27,0:00:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,酷琦 我们没有那么不一样\NCookie, we're not that different.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.71,0:00:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的相信我们可以做到\NI truly believe we can make this work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,唱得很好听 哦 那\NThat was hot. Oh, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.21,0:00:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始你恨我 然后又爱我的不得了\Nfirst you hate me, then you love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.05,0:00:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本不知道\NYou have no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,自己的价值\N... what you're worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.22,0:00:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,对我的攻击就是对\NAn attack on me is an attack
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.22,0:00:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你们每个人的攻击\Non each and every one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.05,0:00:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,卢修斯和安德鲁想要开战\NLucious and Andre Lyon want a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.79,0:00:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们就开战\NSo we war.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:00:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 你觉得这感觉对吗\NYeah, that feel right to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你可以把低音弄得重一些\NI think you could make that bass a little harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.84,0:01:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我们有一段时间没有一起合作了\NLook, I know we haven't worked together in a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.07,0:01:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但我很感激你来了\Nbut I appreciate you coming through.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.54,0:01:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉这将是很了不起的作品\NFeel like this is about to be something big.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.68,0:01:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,想不出来比你更合适的人选\NCouldn't think of anyone better.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.68,0:01:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 拜托 小贾\NOh, come on, Mal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.32,0:01:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我们一起做的音乐有多好\NYou know we make good music together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.32,0:01:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.49,0:01:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 的确很好\NYeah, we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.92,0:01:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们只需要做音乐 德里克\NBut that's all we need to do, Derek.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.84,0:01:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起去杀几个里昂家族的人\NLet's go kill some Lyons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.44,0:01:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你听到了 我们行动吧\NYou heard him. Let's roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.05,0:01:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 你知道我喜欢在上班前和你喝杯咖啡\NNow, you know I love getting coffee with you before work,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但总要有一天\Nbut one of these days,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.06,0:01:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你得让我把咖啡送到你床前\Nyou got to let me bring it to you in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:02:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,哈 虽然 我有可能喜欢这样\NHuh. Well, I might like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,在遥远未来中的某一天\None of these days in the far future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 未来 好吧\NOh, the future, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.64,0:02:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这么不给力 没 没有糖 没有奶油\NCome on. No... no sugar? No cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.47,0:02:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 没有 我喜欢浓的黑咖啡\NOh, no. I like mine dark and strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.47,0:02:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 那么 你还需要改进一下\NAh, well, you're gonna have to do a little better than that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想我们有进一步发展\Nif you want to get in these drawers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里右转\NMake a right right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.75,0:02:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,小心警察\NWatch out for the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.32,0:02:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,确保托尼让他的人散开\NAnd make sure Tony has his guys fan out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.13,0:02:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 先生\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,在那个热狗摊那边\NAnd we got three marks over there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.06,0:02:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,有三个人盯梢\Nat that hot dog stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.56,0:02:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到那个拿着报纸的人了吗\NNow, you see that dude with the newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.07,0:02:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,没人还看印刷的报纸\NNobody reads print anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来都没想过\NI never thought I'd be making
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.44,0:02:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,坐装甲看医生\Ndoctor visits in an armored personnel carrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.41,0:02:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 我了解肖恩 他肯定会报复\NWell, I know Shine; he's gonna clap back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你要想出去\NSo if you want to step your ass out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.51,0:02:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,试试自己是不是防弹的 请便\Nand see if you're bulletproof, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我再试着联系下内莎\NI'ma try Nessa one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.83,0:03:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,又给内莎发信息\NStill texting Nessa again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.76,0:03:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么时候才会弄到手\NWhen you gonna hit that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我会的\NI will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让她见我女儿\NI want her to meet my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,可爱的小孩子 总是能俘获女孩子\NCute little babies, that always gets the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我总以为是你的饶舌技巧让你撩到妹\NI thought it was your rap skills that got the honeys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 也有用\NThat, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.07,0:03:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我要邀请她参加我的现场音乐会\NI'ma invite her to my livestream concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,一但她看到我的表演 就到手了\NOnce she sees me doing my thing, it's game over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那样就够了\NThat's gonna be enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,够了\NPeriod.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,找到他了 是的\NGet him. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.62,0:03:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他的那个贱人也要挨枪子\NAnd that bitch of his gonna catch a few of these, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那你为什么费这么大劲\NSo why are you going through so much trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,宣布你要竞选市长\Nto announce you're running for mayor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.36,0:03:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,要我的话就通知了几个记者 好\NI say just call a couple reporters... Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,宣布一下 然后继续\N... do the damn thing, and keep it moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 我只想对任何他们\NWell, you know, I just want to be prepared
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,问的问题有所准备\Nfor any questions they might throw at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 是的 例如\NOh. Yeah, questions like,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么要和有前科的人约会\Nuh, Why are you trying to date an excon? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 他们可能会问那个 但是 听着 我只会说\NYes, they may ask that. But, look, I'll just say,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.81,0:04:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没到三垒 所以\NI haven't been to third base yet, So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,除非我们往下一步发展 你懂的 今晚就三垒\NUnless we're planning on, you know, changing that tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.15,0:04:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 明天要去见我的假释官\NNo. I got to see my P.O. Tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.19,0:04:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你还在假释期\NYou still have a parole officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 这叫监管释放 所以\NYeah, it's called supervised release, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,小心 议员 不好意思 里昂小姐\NHeads up, Councilman. Excuse me, Ms. Lyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要跟我们走一遭\NYou need to come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,后退 额 我不\NStep back. Uh, no, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不认识你\NI don't even know who the hell you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 让开\NAll right, stand down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.33,0:04:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事 先生们\NWhat's going on here, gentlemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,0:04:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,无意冒犯 议员\NAll due respect, Councilman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人 是你丈夫派我们来的\NYour husband sent us, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,为了你的安全 他不是我丈夫\NFor your own safety. He is not my hu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我们走 夫人 他不是我丈夫\NCome with us, ma'am. He's not my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我不知道他这次做了什么\NLook, I don't know what he did this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,后退 后退\NStay back. Stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,手拿开\NGet your hands off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.11,0:04:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\NI'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,在录音室熬到很晚嘛 兄弟\NLong night at the studio, huh, brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,吃些鸡蛋吧 兄弟\NGet some of these eggs, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.12,0:04:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我做了很多\NI made plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 帅哥\NGood morning, sunshine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.55,0:05:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,唷\NYo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.88,0:05:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,肖恩 你在干什么\NShine, what the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.59,0:05:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么在这里\NWhat the hell are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你和他搞到一起了\NYou smashing this dude?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不管他和他爸对我的所做所为吗\NAfter what him and his father did to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你的淤青是这样来的嘛 安德鲁\NThat's how you got the bruise, Andre?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们发生了点分歧\NWe had a disagreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 我们有分歧\NOh, we had a disagreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 不\NNo, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,肖恩 看着 我\NShine, look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,走开 内莎 看着我\NGet out the way, Nessa. Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我哥哥 我爱你\NYou're my brother, and I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.44,0:05:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有其他亲人了 你知道的\NI ain't got nobody else! You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让你为了这个缠上官司 看着我\NAnd I will not have you catching a case over this. Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.41,0:05:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们离开 肖恩\NLet's go, Shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,肖恩\NShine...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不 肖恩\NNo! Shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会在她面前动手\NI don't get my hands dirty in front of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.99,0:05:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我还会再来的\NBut I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.49,0:06:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上 我会把你留到最后\NIn fact, I think I'll save you for last.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.41,0:06:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 兄弟\NHey, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.34,0:06:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,替我的朋友说声抱歉 兄弟\NSorry about my friends, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候 他们\NSometimes they, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,有点失控\Nthey get out of hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我房子外面的保安是什么情况\NWhat's with all the security outside my spot?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我星期五的直播表演没问题 对吗\NWe're good for my livestream show on Friday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,说不好 哈基姆\NNot exactly, Hakeem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,卢修斯 你怎么不告诉他\NLucious, why don't you tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,像我以前说的 一但肖恩\NAs I was saying, once Shine
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,再进入到我的势力范围\Nreentered into my orbit,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道总有一天\NI knew there was gonna come a time
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.02,0:06:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他需要教训一下\Nin which he needed to be corrected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.59,0:06:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,很幸运的是 昨天晚上\NSo fortunately, last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:06:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我的大儿子和我都认为\Nmy eldest son and I decided
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他的所为是极其不尊重人的\Nthat his actions were extremely disrespectful
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,如果 不加以管教\Nand, if left unchecked,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.67,0:07:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,会威胁到这个家庭 所以我们\Na threat to this family. And so we...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,教训了他一顿\N... checked his ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.91,0:07:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么教训的\NChecked him how?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么教训的\NHow you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,除了肖恩现在在我的地方试图报复\NExcept now Shine is at my place trying to clap back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.88,0:07:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉 贾马尔 不会再有下一次了\NI'm sorry about that, Jamal; it won't happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我会搬到老爸的客房的\NI'm moving in to Pop's guesthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.85,0:07:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不 小安\NNo, Dre.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我 你不会想什么都依赖他\NTrust me, you don't want to be all up under him like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.80,0:07:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 我们现在连朋友都打了\NHold up. We beating up our friends now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,儿子 他不是你朋友\NBoy, he is not your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 你们所有人 我们跟他混在一起\NLook, all of y'all, the only reason why
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.94,0:07:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,的唯一原因是为了阻止塔里克\Nwe are even messing with him is to block Tariq
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,立案告我们 你们明白了吗\Nfrom building a case against us, you got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 我们到底如何要怎么阻止他\NNow, how in the hell are we gonna stop him
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,对我们动真格的\Nfrom flipping out on us now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.61,0:07:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,因为肖恩不是个告密的人\NBecause Shine is not a snitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他情愿死也不会当个告密小人\NHe'd rather be dead than be a rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我发誓 我是唯一一个\NI swear, am I the only one...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,看 你就爱这种闹剧\NSee, you love this type of drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是 他的确是\NYeah, he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是让我的家人又聚在一起了吗\NIt brought my family back together, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,和肖恩一起做的音乐是我最好的一些音乐\NThe music I'm doing with Shine is some of my best stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 你不得不先搁置一段时间了\NWell, you're gonna have to postpone that for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经告诉我的歌迷要发行新歌\NI already told my fans it's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:07:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不管你跟歌迷讲了什么\NI don't care what you told your fans!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:07:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,现场直播不能重来啊 老妈\NAin't no doovers in live streaming, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.47,0:08:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是脑袋中枪了 也没法重来\NThere also ain't no doovers if you get shot in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 听着 不要紧张 没有人要改变任何事\NLook, look, relax. Ain't nobody changing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,所有事情还是按计划来\NEverything stays according to what we're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人只需提高警惕 规规矩矩\NEverybody just needs to be alert and stay in their lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.41,0:08:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,然后等你和那个恶心的议员\NAnd then soon as you're done playing house with...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,玩完过家家\Nthe mayor of Dingleberry,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.25,0:08:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你欠我一支提安娜的单曲\Nyou owe me a Tiana single.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.65,0:08:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,贾马尔 你可以继续\NAnd, Jamal, you can go back to doing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,做在你没做音乐时候做的那些事\Nwhatever you do when you're not making music.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你想帮助这个家 那就帮\NYou want to help the family? You help the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.03,0:08:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你想拯救这个世界 那就拯救世界\NYou want to go and free the world? Free the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 小哈 你的帝国娱乐极度流的表演\NBut, Keem, your Empire XStream show
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,按计划进行\Ngoes on as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须提高订阅者数量\NWe got to keep pushing them stats up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.87,0:08:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,肖恩现在就在我想要他在的地方\NI got Shine exactly where I want him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是时候解决他了\NNow it's time to tuck his little bitch ass in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.79,0:08:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他来了 哈基姆\NThere he is! Hakeem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.63,0:09:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 弟弟\NWhat's up, little brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你对这个曲子有感觉吗\NYou feeling this track?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经知道了\NYou already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,上车\NGet in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,哟 你可以暂停嘛\NYo, can you pause that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哟 你想要\NYo, you want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我要做什么\NWhat I got to do for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,让你的极度流的表演更有卖点 你和我一起\NMake your Empire XStream event a double bill. You and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.02,0:09:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 大哥 这是我自己的秀\NCome on, bro, I'm doing my own jam right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 哈基姆 但是\NNo, I get it, Hakeem. But listen,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以给粉丝们他们在全美金曲奖上错过的\Nwe could give the people what they missed out on at the ASAs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.12,0:09:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,而且实话告诉你 我也很需要这个\NAnd keeping it real, I need it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我要让我的粉丝知道 我还没退出乐坛\NIt's important that I show the fans that I'm still in the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥 你都没法上台表演\NBro, you can't even perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己也清楚 在一大堆\NYou know that. Not in front of
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.13,0:09:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,人面前 还有那些欢呼声下 是不行\Na big crowd with all these bells and whistles, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.99,0:09:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我觉得我们可以在我家客厅表演\NBut I was thinking we could do it at my living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.13,0:09:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,以一种非常亲民的方式\NWe could make it mad intimate
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,给粉丝一个惊喜\Nand just blast it out to the fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,可能吧\NMaybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.50,0:09:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,哈基姆和贾马尔 里昂兄弟\NHakeem and Jamal, the Lyon brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,现场直播\NLive and alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道那句名言吗\NYou know the message that that sends to the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.81,0:10:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们不能为后世所铭记\NWhy we even doing music
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.68,0:10:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那做音乐还有什么意思呢\Nif we don't make a real imprint on the next generations?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这是怎么回事吗\NYou know what this is about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你和爸爸\NYou and Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.82,0:10:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是你想和他结束恶性循环的问题\NThat End the cycle Beef you got with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的\NNah, man,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为你和贝拉\Nit's about you and Bella.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为我们的父亲 她的爷爷\NIt's about the fact that our father... her grandfather...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,打了你最爱的音乐制作人\Nbeat up your favorite producer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的想让她在这样的环境下长大吗\NThat's really the type of world you want her to grow up in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去拉维特克斯\NWe're going to Laviticus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.63,0:10:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 里昂先生\NYes, sir, Mr. Lyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.21,0:10:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 听着\NAll right, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,大家还好吗 我是你们的贾马尔 里昂\NWhat's up, y'all? It's your boy, Jamal Lyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.81,0:10:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我是他的宝贝弟弟 哈基姆\NAnd I'm the smooth baby brother, Hakeem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要宣布一件特别的事\NAnd we have a very special announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,说吧 小哈 不 你来说 小贾\NTell 'em, Keem. Yeah. Nah, you tell 'em, Mal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 这周五 一定要锁定我们\NAll right, look, this Friday make sure y'all are tuned in,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,八点整 我们有一个特别的节目\N8 o'clock... we have a very special event.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.82,0:10:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,美女们 记得刷 #基姆队 一整天\NAnd look, #TeamKeem, all day, ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你们知道那是什么的\NYeah, yeah. Y'all know what that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个小丑\NHey, what kind of funboy stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,在这干什么幼稚的事呢\Ny'all two clowns doing up there, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 这个家伙在\NHey, yo, what this dude doing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的地盘上干嘛呢 哎 等等等等\Nin our spot for, man?! Yo, yo, yo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我在干嘛\NWhat it look like I'm doing, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我是来找你的 你是说唱歌手 挑战我啊\NI'm coming at you. You a MC. Battle me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:10:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在就想挑战我吗 小子 小哈\NWhat, you want to go right now, little man? Keem...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我们当着你粉丝的面对决\NNo, let's do it in front of your subscribers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.90,0:11:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们看看\NLet them enjoy the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.24,0:11:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我也会带上我的粉丝\NI'ma bring my subscribers, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.21,0:11:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我设计了自己的流媒体应用还有等等\NI designed my own little streaming apps and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.94,0:11:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不需要老爹的钱来做这些事\NI didn't need daddy money for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.51,0:11:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我是个绅士\NBut since I'm a gentleman,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,所以下面就是我会对你做的事 听着\Nthat's what I'ma do for you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.32,0:11:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我会让你在几秒钟之内\NI'ma have you bloody and trending worldwide
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,就在全世界面前血流成河\Nin a matter of seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,对镜头笑一笑 你们都喜欢自拍 不是吗\NSay Cheese For the camera. Y'all like selfies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是 为粉丝什么都行\NYeah, anything for the fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢你了\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.42,0:11:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要走了\NWe're gonna leave, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去找他谈谈 等等 别去 过来\NI got to go talk to him. Wait, stop. Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.03,0:11:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你比他好多了 我们都是\NYou are better than that. We are better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我\NLook at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,用点脑子 行不行\NStart using your mind, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,有这么多保镖\NHow the hell did he even get up in here
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么还能上来这里\Nwith all of this security around?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.71,0:11:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,卢修斯\NLucious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有了首很棒的新歌\NSo, we have that great new song,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,星光 提安娜很喜欢\NStarlight. Tiana loves it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得是时候录歌了\Nand I think it's time to record it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我不觉得这能作为主打单曲\NWell, I don't think it's a lead single.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,她在拉维特克斯唱的那首歌\NNow, the song she did at Laviticus is
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,热度已经很高了 而且数据显示\Nalready getting crazy heat. And the numbers show...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能不能先不提数据\NCan we just stop with the numbers really quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我和提安娜谈过了 那首歌不是她想要的\NI actually spoke to Tiana, and that song is not what she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.39,0:11:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,贝基 艺人监理部不能总是\NWell, Becky, in A&R, we can't always
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:11:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,让步于艺人的想法\Ngive in to what the artist wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,别用这种语气和我说话\NDo not mansplain to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是别以这种白人的口气和我说话\NAnd especially do not whitemansplain to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就别这么无知\NThen don't be uninformed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这个消息能让你好受点的话\NNow, if it makes you feel better,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以在专辑里\Nwe can throw an experimental track
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.27,0:12:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,加上一首实验歌曲 首先 这个不关乎我的感受\Ndeeper in the album. This isn't about how I feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,其次 我不同意\Nfirst of all, and secondly, I disagree...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的一切\Nwith everything that you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 先把枪都放下\NOkay. Let's put down the guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NAll right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.58,0:12:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这位屋顶上的小提琴手说的有道理\NFiddler on the Roof here has a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他更有远见\NHe's looking at the bigger picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我也同意他说的\NAnd I agree with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,提安娜唱的那首歌热度的确很高\NThat song Tiana did is getting crazy heat,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们就要录那首歌 好吗\Nso that is the song we will record. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 让我们握手言和吧\NAll right, now, can't we just all get along?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,亲亲抱抱\NKiss and make up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,千万别\NDon't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,内莎\NNessa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你能来\NThanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧\NYou okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 我\NYeah, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,到底发生什么了 小安\NWhat the hell is going on, Dre?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.28,0:12:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得你和我上床了\NYou think you can just hook up with me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.65,0:12:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就能背着我去\Nand then not tell me that you just got done
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.52,0:12:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,蹂躏我的好朋友吗\Nstomping out my best friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就是这样的关系吗 我应该告诉你的\NThat's what we doing? I should've told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.99,0:12:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我无能为力\NI couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们现在怎么办\NSo what do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.19,0:13:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,卢修斯想和肖恩坐下来好好谈谈\NLucious wants to have a sitdown with Shine
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,让事情回到正轨\Nand get things back on track.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 坐下来谈\NWhat? A sit...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.63,0:13:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证 内莎\NI promise you, Nessa,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不会再找他麻烦的\Nwe're not gonna screw him over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,最好别 小安\NYou better not, Dre.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.97,0:13:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他是我唯一的亲人了\NBecause he's all I got.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,过来 不\NCome here. N...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,过来 过来 过来\NCome here. Come here. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你只有他一个亲人了\NI respect that he's all you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.79,0:13:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以有更多的\NYou could have more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你来看我的时候说的话\NWhat you said when you came to see me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能有我的音乐天赋\Nif you had my musical talent...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么意思\Nwhat did you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我把肖恩找过来谈谈\NHelp me get Shine to the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我就告诉你那是什么意思\NI'll show you what I meant by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.04,0:13:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 小哈 你准备好了\NAll right, Keem, you ready to put...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.05,0:13:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,见到我很惊讶吗\NYou look surprised to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,惊讶\NSurprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.25,0:14:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,见到我的儿子我就开心 即使不是我想见的那个\NBut happy to see my son, even if it's the wrong one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.52,0:14:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我有个好消息\NWell, look, I have good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,哈基姆正在努力忘掉他和格拉姆之间的不愉快\NHakeem is squashing that little pettyass beef with Gram.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我\NSo, yes, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.53,0:14:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我失去了芙蕾达 但是我不会再失去哈基姆\NI lost Freda, but... I'm not losing Hakeem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛要往自己住的玻璃房砸砖头呢 儿子\NWhy are you throwing bricks when you live in a glass house, son?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.94,0:14:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你难道忘了 你为了把芙蕾达\NHave you forgotten all those lies you told
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,弄出来而撒的那些谎了吗\Nin order to get Freda out of that place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.41,0:14:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我做了我该做的事 是啊 然后\NI did what I had to do. Yeah, and then
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,又把她给扔回贫民窟去\Nyou dropped her ass back off in the projects.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,莎士比亚说过\NYou know, Shakespeare said,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须对自己诚实\NTo thy own self be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你越快接受自己就是年轻版的我的\NThe sooner you accept that you are the younger version of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.45,0:14:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,升级版本 你就越快能重回\Nwith a twist... the sooner you'll be
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,舞台 像你以前一样\Nback on that stage and be your old self again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.89,0:14:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这个地方\NIt's this space, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.70,0:14:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,上次我坐这把椅子的时候 我和妈妈反目\NLast time I sat in this chair, I turned against my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,因为她活该\NBecause she deserved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那你呢\NAnd what do you deserve?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.60,0:14:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么变得如此堕落的\NHow you get so corrupt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你不可能天生就是这样的\NThere's no way that you were born this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:15:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,贾马尔 你生来就有50%的预设基因会让你变成我\NJamal, you are 50% genetically predisposed to become me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这是无法避免的\NIt's inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我喜欢小哈什么吗\NYou know what I like about Keem?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.22,0:15:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他知道他和我喜欢的东西一样\NHe knows that he likes what I like,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他清楚他会变得和我一样\Nand he knows he's going to become me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他只知道你告诉他的\NHe knows nothing except what you told him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你该放手让他做自己想成为的人\NMaybe you should let him be the man he wants to be
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是变成你期望的那种人\Ninstead of the man that you want him to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪 小贾 你太老套了\NOh, my God, you are so corny, Mal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.16,0:15:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,只要上帝同意 我都准备帮你预约\NI'ma book a duet with you and Mary Magdalene,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,和抹大拉的玛利亚合唱了\Nsoon as God gives me the okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.47,0:15:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 我(上帝)不同意\NOops. I said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.18,0:15:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,美女 你好啊\NHey, girl. How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你真漂亮 是不是瘦了\NYou look good! You lost weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,胡里欧 我的朋友 哦\NJulio, my man. Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,夏莲娜 霍落威\NSharlene! Holloway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 美女 我买了你最爱吃的\NHey, girl, I bought you your favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,省省吧 你迟到了 什么\NKeep it. You're late. Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.90,0:15:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你预约是早上九点 现在已经九点四十五了\NYour appointment was 9:00 a.M. It's a quarter to 10:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 但是我每次都是这个时候来的\NI know, but I always come here at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.11,0:16:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来有点生气 我能做点什么吗\NYou seem a little off. Is there something I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你的监管释放明确规定了\NThe rules of your supervised release stipulate that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你要迟到 必须要提前联系我\Nyou need to contact me if you're going to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把这次记下来\NI'm gonna have to write you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么了 夏莲娜\NWhat's going on, Sharlene?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白你的意思\NI don't know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,上次我来这的时候\NWell, the last time I was here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.73,0:16:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你还给我看了你孩子的照片\Nyou were showing me pictures of your kids, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你这次的态度却截然不同\Nnow you're acting brandnew.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,说到那件事\NAbout that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你上次来这儿都是三个月之前的事了\NYour last visit was three months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你看不懂时间 我们就要让你\NSince you can't tell time, we're going to have to have you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,每周来这里报道三次\Nreport here three times a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.24,0:16:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,夏莲娜 别这样 拜托\NOh! Sharlene, no, come on, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.98,0:16:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我要经营公司\NYou know I run a company.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我没法一周来三次\NI can't come here three times a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是在和某些暴徒说唱歌手\NThis isn't some thug rapper
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,谈条件 霍落威\Nyou're negotiating with, Holloway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.05,0:16:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是美国政府\NThis is the United States government.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.13,0:16:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是需要时间考虑\NYou need time to consider,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.50,0:17:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以把你送回丹伯里监狱慢慢考虑\NI can send you back to Danbury to think it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 你要去趟厕所\NRight now, you need to use the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.15,0:17:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们赶快解决这个吧\NLet's just get this over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.19,0:17:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你们都不想来录我这首歌\NI know you're not excited to come in to record Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 这是酷琦要求的\NI get it... it's what Cookie wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我告诉你 你来这实际上是\NWhat if I told you that you're actually here
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,录制星光的呢\Nto record Starlight
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这将是你的主打单曲\Nbecause it's about to be your lead single?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 酷琦不是说\NWhat? I thought Cookie said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 我 我说服她了\NNo, I... I talked her out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.94,0:17:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉她你会进录音室\NI told her that you were gonna get in that booth
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,把这首歌做得很棒\Nand slay the hell out of that song,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,然后她就同意了\Nand she... agreed with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.68,0:17:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你说真的吗 百分百真的\NAre you serious? Dead serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 太感谢你了\NOh, my God! Yo, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好了\NYou're the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.52,0:17:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我就像你背后的内衣扣一样支持你 亲爱的\NYou know I got your back like bra straps, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.52,0:17:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哟\NYo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:17:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我总是懂你想要的 没错\NI'ma always get you what you want. Yeah! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,过去 我曾以仁爱的名义乞求一块面包\NI asked for bread in the name
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,人们却对我置之不理\NOf love and mercy, but humanity did not heed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.14,0:18:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,今后我要用邪恶的名义去夺取\NSo now I shall take it in the name of evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,她怎么老在睡觉\NWhy's she always sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,小孩子就是这样的 儿子\N'Cause that's what babies do, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他们喜欢睡觉\NThey sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.15,0:18:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但你没办法这么做\NBut you can't afford to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 作为这个家族的长者\NYou see, as a patriarch of the family,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你的责任就是去\Nyou're responsible for
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,教导你的下一代们如何在这个冰冷的世界里存活下去\Nteaching your young ones how to survive in this cold world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.19,0:18:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,贾马尔不懂\NJamal don't understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他觉得这个世界都是\NHe thinks it's all
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.90,0:18:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,康巴(歌颂人权的赞歌)和爱 但是他错了\NKumbaya and love, but he's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.07,0:18:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是杀戮 或被杀戮\NIt's kill or be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是吞噬 或被吞噬\NEat or be eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.87,0:18:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我知道你努力\NLook, I know you're trying
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,想教导我在你手下\Nto get me up under you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,像是安德鲁在你手下那样\Nlike how you got Andre up under you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你把格拉姆给灭了\NI want you to crush Gram
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这能给帝国娱乐赚很多钱\Nbecause it means money for Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,并且帝国娱乐极度流也需要这些\Nand Empire XStream needs that kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,吹嘘和炒作\Nfanfare and activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我要你把他毁了\NBut I want you to destroy him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你是里昂家族的一员\N'cause you're a Lyon,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我要让全世界知道\Nand I want the world to know
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人能玩弄你\Nthat you're not someone to be trifled with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.26,0:19:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我要这个小女孩知道他的父亲是怎样的一个人\NI want this little girl to know what kind of man her daddy is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.37,0:19:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么每个人都要把贝拉牵扯进来\NWhy is everybody bringing Bella into this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.53,0:19:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,因为 像你一样\NBecause, like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,她出生在里昂家\Nshe was born a Lyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.71,0:19:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,所以她生下来就已经被牵扯进去了\NSo she's born into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.54,0:19:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,看到这本书了吗\NSee this book?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,卡里 纪伯伦写的\NIt's written by Kahlil Gibran.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,叫作 泪与笑\NIt's called A Tear and a Smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,里面有一个罪犯的故事\NInside it is the story of The Criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.42,0:19:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,讲到一个年轻男人\NIt tells of a young man...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,非常热心的一个人\Nwho was very kind of heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.29,0:19:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他依靠着他的善良 与人道\Nand he depended on the kindness of humanity
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.90,0:19:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,想要混口饭吃\Nin order for him to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但过不了多久 他就发现他快要饿死了\NBut after some time, he found himself starving to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,然后就在你觉得他差不多要死去的时候\NAnd right when you thought he was about to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.31,0:19:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他意识到了他自己真正的天性\Nhe realized his own true nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.64,0:19:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,看看 小基 人类的本性\NYou see, Keem, the nature of humanity isn't
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.81,0:20:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不是爱与和平 而是黑暗和残暴\Nlove and peaceful, it's dark and beastly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.02,0:20:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,它将温顺与谦和推向罪恶\NAnd it'll turn the meek and the humble into a criminal,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.29,0:20:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,和平之子则成为\Nand the sons of peace into...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,毁灭人的毁灭者\Ndestroyers of men.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他变成了毁灭人的毁灭者\NHe became a destroyer of men.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他不得不这么做\NBecause he had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.37,0:21:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这是\NWhat is... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.99,0:22:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 一个问题 你能别这样表演吗\NUm, one, can you not do the stool like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.39,0:22:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这让你看起来像是要发飙\NIt makes you look pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.86,0:22:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,还有就是 你真心跑到界外去了\NAnd then also, you are literally out of bounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.09,0:22:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这是这场表演的目的\NThat's what all this tape is for.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.46,0:22:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在看起来就像是 在我的阳台上\NYou're, like, in my balcony.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.56,0:22:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,整个表演太软弱了\NYo, this whole performance is too soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.60,0:22:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,它需要给人肃然起敬的感觉 小贾\NIt needs to command respect, Mal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你现在说话和卢修斯一样\NYo, why you sounding like Lucious now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.47,0:22:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,哈基姆 我们明天就要表演了 好吗\NHakeem, our performance is tomorrow, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.61,0:22:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他们重新安排了我的整个公寓 我们有一首歌\NThey're rearranging my entire apartment, and we have a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,一首酷毙了的歌 这是酷毙了 但是这一段\NA dope song. It is dope, but this verse,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.31,0:22:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要用来回击所有和我作对的人\NI need to use to clap back to my haters.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.61,0:22:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你不需要\NNo, you should not.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.75,0:22:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 如果你打算今后的\NYou know what, you're literally
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.48,0:22:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,整个音乐生涯都去做回击唱片\Ngonna stand your whole career doing clapback records.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.58,0:22:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 我不在乎\NThat's fine, and I don't care,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.69,0:22:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但是请你在别人的音乐里做这些\Nbut do it on someone else's track,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.15,0:22:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,因为 我不允许你放这种鬼话在我这儿\N'cause you're not gonna put that B.S. On mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.99,0:22:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们签协议了吗\NWe got terms and conditions?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你有足够的粉丝\NIf you had enough followers,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.03,0:23:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你就可以在你自己的频道做这些 而不是帝国娱乐极度流这里\Nyou'd be doing this on your own channel, not Empire XStream.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.79,0:23:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 老弟 你快惹恼我了\NYou know what, bro, you about to piss me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.00,0:23:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,哥 你是才需要这个节目的人 不是我\NBro, you're the one that needs this, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.77,0:23:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你是掉粉过气的那个 不是我\NYou're the one that's losing his fans, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 如果需要签约的话\NNow, if it's gonna be terms and conditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.10,0:23:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,想想看吧 那也得按照我的条件\Njust think about it... it's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.37,0:23:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,因为 众所周知\N'Cause everybody knows
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.84,0:23:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这场音乐会决定着你的生死\Nthis concert is life or death for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.84,0:23:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,想想看吧\NJust think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,举起手\NArms up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.17,0:23:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 不用这样吧 兄弟 如果我带了武器\NHey, come on, man. Hey, if I was packing,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.07,0:23:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我就违背了坐下来谈的条件了\NI would have violated the terms of the sitdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.17,0:23:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这是对我的侵犯\NThis is a violation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.34,0:23:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我想要侵犯你\NIf I wanted to violate you,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.11,0:23:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,肖恩 你会被顶着抢搜身\NShine, you'd be getting patted down with some bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.91,0:23:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,呵 是嘛\NYeah. Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.54,0:23:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我有四个枪手在外头说\NWell, I got four shooters outside
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.85,0:23:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你不敢这么干\Nthat say you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.95,0:23:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你只有三个\NNo, you got three.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.35,0:23:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一个在五星酒店里\NOne stayed back at a fivestar hotel,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.58,0:23:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,现在应该正在享受我送去的客房服务\Nwhere he's getting some room service sent up by me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.52,0:24:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你喜欢的话 我现在可以给你在外面的兄弟\NAnd if you like, I can send your boys outside
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.02,0:24:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,也送点点心\Na snack, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.42,0:24:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,别忘记我也是做这个的 肖恩\NDon't forget I do this, Shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.66,0:24:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你不是做这个的 卢修斯\NNo, you don't do this, Lucious.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.53,0:24:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我做这个\NI do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.86,0:24:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你多年没做了\NYou ain't did this for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.83,0:24:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你有了事业 而我还在混街头\NYou industry. And I'm still in the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.27,0:24:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我必须要毁掉某人的话\NAnd if I got to blow somebody up,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.97,0:24:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我不介意同归于尽\NI don't care if I die with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.80,0:24:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你已经知道了\NBut you already know this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.94,0:24:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 也许我们的开头\NLook, maybe we got off
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.61,0:24:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不太顺利\Non the wrong foot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.44,0:24:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,喝点什么吗\NYou want a drink or something, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.38,0:24:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不了 有话直说\NNo, I'm straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.78,0:24:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可能会艰难地谈一晚上\N'Cause we can talk tough all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.72,0:24:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但我记得之前\NBut last time I checked,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.16,0:24:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们和内莎之间的进展很好\Nwe had something real good going with Nessa.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.92,0:24:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 我也这么觉得\NYeah, I thought so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.99,0:24:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,在你和你儿子试图离间和攻击之前是的\NThat's until you and your son tried to divide and conquer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.02,0:24:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你自找上门的\NYou came at us first, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.36,0:24:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么\NWhat is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.66,0:24:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在做什么\NWhat are we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.56,0:24:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,算了吧 卢修斯 是我 兄弟\NCome on, Lucious, it's me, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.00,0:24:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我本应该早就埋了你的\NI could have buried you a long time ago
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.00,0:24:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,用任意一个现在已经变成尸体的人\Nwith any one of them bodies you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.84,0:24:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你忘记卡姆登了吗\NYou forget Camden?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.67,0:24:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 兄弟\NHold on, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.07,0:24:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你可是在跟我说话\NIt's me you're talking to.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.91,0:24:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,口口声声叫我 兄弟\NCalling me Bro,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.08,0:24:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,却要提起这样的事\Nand you're gonna bring something like that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.71,0:24:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这些我完全不知道是什么东西的事情\NWhich I don't know what the hell you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.51,0:25:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不过如果我确实知道\NBut if I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.25,0:25:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那这就是违反谈判规定了\Nthat would be violating code right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.82,0:25:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好 你知道吗\NOkay, you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.25,0:25:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在浪费我的时间\NThis is a waste of my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.89,0:25:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,算了吧 内莎 我们走\NCome on, Nessa, let's move.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.89,0:25:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,肖恩 嘿 我听说你来了\NShine. Hey, I thought I heard you in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.73,0:25:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,把我女儿都吵醒了\Nwaking up my baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.86,0:25:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,阿妮卡 我们事情正谈到一半\NLook, Anika, we in the middle of something right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.76,0:25:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 好的 你和他说过我们讨论过的事情了吗\NOh, good. Did you tell him about the idea that we discussed?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.07,0:25:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我的好老公\NMy husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.50,0:25:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,就在不久前 我们刚刚说到\Njust the other day, he had just said
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.27,0:25:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他有多么感谢能有你在他身边\Nhow much he really appreciates having you around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.87,0:25:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 帮哈基姆做音乐\NYou know, putting your ear to Hakeem,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.71,0:25:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,带来内莎\Nbringing in Nessa.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.11,0:25:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他甚至说真的很惭愧\NHe even said that it was such a shame
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.54,0:25:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你的才能被埋没了这么久\Nthat your talent had been slept on all this time, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.91,0:25:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,想象一下你要是有自己的团队能做什么\Nimagine what you could do with your own imprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.02,0:25:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 宝贝\NRight, babe?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.92,0:25:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 你知道 我是说 如果你需要人\NBut, you know, I mean, if you ever need somebody
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.12,0:25:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,帮你跨过一些障碍 我就在这儿\Nto bounce anything off of, I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.26,0:25:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管告诉我\NJust let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.23,0:25:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,很开心见到你\NGood to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.43,0:25:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的条件么 卢修斯\NIs that what you're offering, Lucious?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.23,0:25:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己的团队\NMy own imprint?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.10,0:25:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚正想说这件事\NThat's what I was trying to get to
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.97,0:26:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你就已经变身金刚了 兄弟\Nwhen you came charging in like King Kong or something, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.28,0:26:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,内莎也是交易的一部分吗\NIs Nessa part of that deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.04,0:26:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 内莎和帝国娱乐已经签的合同和这个不同 但是\NLook, Nessa's under a different contract with Empire, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.05,0:26:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以两相结合\Nwe can crosspollinate, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.05,0:26:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,芙蕾达 盖茨呢\NWhat about Freda Gatz?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.42,0:26:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说她退出了\NI heard she out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.09,0:26:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说她很厉害\NI hear she's dope.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.16,0:26:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 如果芙蕾达能为你所用 那她自然是你的 兄弟\NHey, if Freda gets it done for you, she's all yours, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.83,0:26:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,芙蕾达很赞 肖恩\NFreda's the one, Shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.57,0:26:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这对你来说是个很好的交易\NAnd this could be a good deal for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.17,0:26:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,对我而言\NOh, for me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.07,0:26:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,对我们大家 肖恩\NFor us, Shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.44,0:26:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,成交\NWe got a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.61,0:26:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎加入帝国娱乐 亲爱的\NWelcome to the Empire, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.35,0:26:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你还好吗 我差不多结束了\NHey, you okay? I barely got through,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.45,0:26:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 最后两个会议\Nuh, last two meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.99,0:26:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我的假释官见过了吗\NYou been talking to my probation officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.36,0:26:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 没有啊\NSay what? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.70,0:26:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要我做这个\NWhy would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.83,0:26:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 这完全是一个巧合 在我和你说完\NSo, it's a total coincidence that after I tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.37,0:27:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我处在监管释放状态之后\NI'm on supervised release,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.90,0:27:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我的假释官就开始对我执行严格的监管了吗\Nmy P.O. Starts acting strict with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.54,0:27:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我真的一点都不知道 不是我\NNo, I don't know nothing about that. It's not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.81,0:27:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 那一定是因为你在竞选市长\NHmm. Then it must be because you're running for mayor
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.34,0:27:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你想要我在你控制之下\Nand you want to keep me in check.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.18,0:27:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 听着\NOh, uh, okay, look,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.85,0:27:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有控制女人的习惯\NI don't make a habit of keeping women in check.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.88,0:27:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你把我和你的前夫弄混淆了\NYou must've got me confused with your exhusband.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.72,0:27:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,别提卢修斯\NLeave Lucious out of this, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.12,0:27:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 怎么可能不\NWell, how can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.62,0:27:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定\NHe's making sure
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.79,0:27:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,和这件事脱不了干系\Nhe's very much a part of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.16,0:27:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是什么意思 安吉洛\NAnd what the hell is that supposed to mean, Angelo?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.36,0:27:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,酷琦 听着 我想要理解你 我知道你也知道\NCookie, look, I'm feeling you. Okay, I know you know this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.07,0:27:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你和卢修斯\NBut you and Lucious,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.80,0:27:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你们之间很多问题都还没有解决 你需要考虑这些\Ny'all got some unresolved issues you need to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.34,0:27:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我唯一的问题就是被告知我有问题\NMy only issue is being told what issues I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.04,0:27:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 安吉洛\NSee, Angelo,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.68,0:27:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本不了解我 我不了解 我怎么可能了解\Nyou don't know me like that. I don't. How can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.74,0:27:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本没让我了解 每次我尝试\NYou don't let me. Every time I try
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.31,0:27:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,走近你 你总是把我挡在墙外\Nto get close to you, you put a wall up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.08,0:27:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 看 就是这样\NAw, man... See? Look, there you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.92,0:27:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能 好吧\NI can't! What? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.18,0:27:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那今晚就先这样吧\NUh, let's just cut this night short,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.75,0:27:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我们现在说话都比较轻率\Nall right, 'cause we're both getting reckless in the mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.59,0:27:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那是 我们中的某个人会说一些\NYeah. ... and one of us is gonna say something
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.26,0:27:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会后悔的话\Nthat we're gonna regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.49,0:27:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经说了\NAlready did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.33,0:28:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安，酷琦\NGood night, Cookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.90,0:28:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，晚安\NYeah, well, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.70,0:28:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 祝你好运\NThank you. Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.98,0:28:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.11,0:28:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是没有听从直接的命令\NYet you still disobeyed a direct order,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.65,0:28:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你跟提安娜撒谎了\Nand you lied to Tiana.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.98,0:28:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是蛇爬滑梯游戏\NThis ain't Chutes and Ladders.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.45,0:28:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,而是音乐生意\NIt's the music business.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.29,0:29:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你们应该懂我说的生意是什么意思\NI thought you people understood what the word Business Meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.82,0:29:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 酷琦会很生气的\NYou know, Cookie is going to be pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.86,0:29:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 这就是为什么我要你先听听这首歌\NI know. That's why I wanted you to listen to the song first.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.76,0:29:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你能帮我劝劝酷琦这歌真的会非常火\NYou can help me convince Cookie that this song is a hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.80,0:29:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道它有多火 不不不，你知道的\NI don't know that it is a hit. Yes, you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.00,0:29:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这歌很棒 你听听\NThe song is dope. Listen to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.63,0:29:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,更重要的是，这是艺人自己想要的\NMore importantly, it's what the artist wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.34,0:29:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们明天要做的就是让酷琦听听这歌\NAll we have to do is let Cookie hear it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.34,0:29:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,她会喜欢的，所有账都会一笔勾销的\NShe'll love it, and all will be forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.81,0:29:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,听听她唱的\NListen to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.36,0:29:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把我清洁工的号码给你\NI'ma give you the number to my cleaning lady,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.63,0:29:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这地方太恶心了 哈基姆\Nbecause this place is disgusting, Hakeem.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.49,0:29:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该早知道有一天你会跑回去找妈妈的\NI should've known you would have ran to Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.90,0:29:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,都这么大的人了\NSo much for being a grownup.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.47,0:29:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我给她演了我的歌\NYeah, I played her the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.87,0:29:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是 那歌很火 你得照\NYes, and it's fire, and you will do it
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.04,0:29:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,贾马尔和你计划的那样表演 就这样\Nthe way you and Jamal arranged it, end of story.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.50,0:29:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你们还能强迫我吗\NHow you gonna make me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.21,0:29:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你能不能不要像个孩子一样 你才是小孩\NWhy don't you stop acting like a baby. You the baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.44,0:29:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你才是 你个乳臭未干的小孩 你就这样了\NYou the baby, the dumb little baby... that's what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.44,0:29:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你个地中海秃头小孩\NAnd you the semibaldheadedlooking baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.65,0:29:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴\NShut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.95,0:30:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 我面前站着谁 两个男孩还是两个女孩\NNow, what did I have, two boys or two little girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.95,0:30:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你们听起来像两个娘炮\N'Cause y'all sound like two sissies.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.69,0:30:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 我在投资者展示会回去的路上说了什么\NNow, what did I tell y'all way back at that investor showcase?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.79,0:30:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 你们不该做的就是\NHmm? What y'all not gonna do is come in between
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.03,0:30:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,挡我的财路\Nme and my money.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.70,0:30:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你们哥俩已经很久\NNow, it's been too long since you and your brother
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.87,0:30:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没在人前表演了\Nperformed in front of the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.23,0:30:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是粉丝所要的\NAnd that's what they want,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.27,0:30:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是我们要给他们的\Nand that's what we will give them.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.57,0:30:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你们就是想把我硬拉入\NY'all just trying to drag me
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.37,0:30:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你们与卢修斯之间的矛盾\Ninto a fight y'all are having with Lucious.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.24,0:30:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你特么给我滚过来 小子\NGet your narrow ass back up here, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.87,0:30:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,别在我说话的时候走开\NDon't you ever walk away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.58,0:30:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我在试着阻止一个儿子\NI'm trying to stop one son
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.05,0:30:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,去回击一个根本都不是我们厂牌的艺人\Nfrom clapping back at an artist that's not even on our label.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.78,0:30:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,哼 哼\NMmhmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.59,0:30:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,噢，我只是在试着\NOh. And I'm only trying
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.09,0:30:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我另一个傻儿子\Nto help my other son get back to performing
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.42,0:30:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,在他的粉丝忘记他这号人之前\Nin front of his fans before they forget
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.22,0:30:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,重回舞台表演\Nhow much they love his stupid ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.26,0:30:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯哼\NMmhmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.13,0:30:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你害怕\NIf you are afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.83,0:30:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,跟着你爸爸对着干\Nof getting on the wrong side of your daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.27,0:30:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那你也绝对不会想要跟你妈妈对着干\Nyou don't want to get on the wrong side of your mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.34,0:30:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,懂了吗\NYou feel me?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.71,0:31:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 你听懂我的话没\NI said, do you feel me?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.27,0:31:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是 我懂了\NYeah, I feel you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.88,0:31:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 过来\NGood. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.61,0:31:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NMmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.58,0:31:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 老妈\NHey, Ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.05,0:31:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,把这该死的地方弄干净\NClean this damn place up.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.72,0:31:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,闻起来跟屎一样\NSmelling like ass in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.89,0:31:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,下一次 进我的房子请拖鞋好吗\NNext time, take your shoes off in my house, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.96,0:31:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴，哈基姆 你最好在我往这儿扔炸弹之前\NShut up, Hakeem. Boy, you better clean this place up before
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.03,0:31:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,把这儿弄干净 猪屎窝\NI throw an acid bomb in here. Nastyass pigsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.00,0:31:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样 大家 我是贾马尔 里昂\NWhat's up, everybody? It's your boy, Jamal Lyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.63,0:31:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我想对你们的观看说谢谢\NI want to say thank you so much for tuning in.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.97,0:31:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在正在帝国极度流上直播\NWe are all the way live on Empire XStream.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.64,0:31:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的弟弟 哈基姆\NThat's my baby brother, Hakeem.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.74,0:31:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在这儿真的只为了爱和光明\NWe are here truly for love and light.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.01,0:31:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,所以为了你们 这首歌献给大家\NSo for all of y'all, this is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.84,0:32:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,谁都能在洗澡的时候\NAnybody can perform in the shower
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.74,0:32:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,或者是在他该死的客厅里表演\Nor in the middle of his damn living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.45,0:32:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,看看这个\NLook at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.61,0:32:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么 用户吗\NWhat are those, the users?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.88,0:32:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来数字正在平稳上升\NLooks like the numbers are staying steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.52,0:32:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，但是他们得继续往上冲才行\NYeah, but they need to go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.05,0:32:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,哈基姆的观众都没在看\NHakeem's audience ain't even tuning in
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.89,0:32:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们不是来这听什么人权颂歌的\Nbecause they not here for this Kumbaya crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.56,0:32:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要来点劲爆的\NWe need some fire in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.12,0:33:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 随便 卢修斯 离我远点\NOkay, whatever, Lucious. Get away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.13,0:33:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.93,0:33:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,格拉姆怎么了\NWhat happened to Gram, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.90,0:33:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,里昂家的人不会从争斗中逃跑 我们要碾压他\NLyons don't run from beef. We crush that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.20,0:33:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想和一个胆小鬼争 而且争的还是我前任\NI don't need to be beefing over a chick who's my ex.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.14,0:33:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其在我马上要有新欢的时候\NEspecially when I'm about to have a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.64,0:33:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.87,0:33:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,内莎\NNessa?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.08,0:33:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯哼 我们谈了一会儿\NYeah. We been talking for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.81,0:33:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天就要把这事儿定下来\NI'ma lock it down today.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.45,0:33:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我不想告诉你这个坏消息\NWell, I hate to be the one to break it to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.81,0:33:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你的兄弟已经捷足先登了\Nbut your brother already got that on lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.58,0:33:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我哥\NMy brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.59,0:33:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不是贾马尔\NNot Jamal.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.29,0:33:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,安德鲁\NDre.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.96,0:33:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不 安德鲁不会那样做的\NNah, Andre wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.96,0:33:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,快把你的女孩追回来\NMan, you better get your girl back.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.83,0:33:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 哥们\NCome on, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.02,0:34:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这是直播 孩子 无论他在生气什么\NThis is live, boy. Whatever he's mad at,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.49,0:34:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,让他气 否则场面会更糟 知道吗\Nlet him be mad, or it's gonna get worse, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.81,0:35:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这怎么回事 哈基姆 这算怎么一回事\NWhat the hell was that, Hakeem?! What the hell was that about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.25,0:35:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你明知道安德鲁搞上了我的女人\NYou got us doing this Mickey Mouse performance
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.52,0:35:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,却还找我来做这像米老鼠一样\Nabout brotherhood when you know
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.92,0:35:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟合家欢的傻逼演出\NAndre's giant ass crushing my girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.89,0:35:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你特么到底在说什么\NWhat the hell are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.32,0:35:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,安德鲁和内莎\NAndre and Nessa!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.69,0:35:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我说的 哈基姆\NThat's what I'm talking about! Hakeem,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.19,0:35:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以找个另外的时间谈这个\Nwe could have talked about this at a different time.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.69,0:35:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你还想否认\NYou're trying to deny it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.16,0:35:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静点 好吗 我甚至都不知道你对内莎有意思\NCalm down, okay? I didn't even know you were into Nessa.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.90,0:35:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你当然知道 我什么都不知道\NOf course you knew! I didn't know nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.40,0:35:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 等等 等等 你们都在干什么\NWait, wait, wait, what are y'all doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.03,0:35:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 不 不 不 不 不 不 不 我无所谓\NNo, no, no, no, no, no! No, no! I don't give a damn
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.57,0:35:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你在生气什么\Nwhat you are pissed off about.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.84,0:35:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在把这事儿完全升级了 我想知道为什么\NYou took it to another level, and I want to know why!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.14,0:35:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这傻逼的演出一开始就是你的主意\NWackass performance was your idea in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.01,0:35:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我就不应该听你的话\NI shouldn't have never listened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.04,0:35:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是利用我做了一场表演\NYou just used me to do a performance
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.55,0:35:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,就因为你没种出去自己表演\N'cause you can't get out there and do it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.25,0:35:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,傻逼还想当真说唱歌手 我现在就杀了你\NFakeass wannabe MC! I will kill you right...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.88,0:35:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,闭上你的狗屎嘴 作法自毙的人\NShut your big ass up, Frankenstein!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.39,0:35:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,加油 加油\NCome on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.52,0:35:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,继续录 不要停\NKeep rolling! Keep filming!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.55,0:35:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不 停\NNo, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.22,0:35:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,关掉\NTurn it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.42,0:35:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底什么毛病\NWhat the hell is wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.76,0:35:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,来人把这个插回去\NSomebody plug this back in!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.19,0:35:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能只抱怨我 哈基姆 啥事都没有\NYou cannot just claim me, Hakeem... nothing happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.06,0:35:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有一起唱那个二重唱 我们气场不合么\NWe didn't do that duet together? We didn't vibe together?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.03,0:35:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天哪 气场 气场 闭嘴\NOh my goodness, a vibe, a vibe! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.57,0:35:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不要担心\NY'all, it's okay, don't worry about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.10,0:35:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,因为哈基姆里昂 他只是在对某位女性\N'cause Hakeem Lyon, he was just vibin'
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.94,0:35:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,散发气场 所以没事\Nto some female, so it's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.94,0:36:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,把摄像机关了 这都结束了\NTurn these cameras off! This is over! A wrap!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.81,0:36:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人都出去\NEverybody out!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.08,0:36:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,小贱人\NPettyass dumb bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.58,0:36:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,闭上你愚蠢的臭嘴\NShut your Frank Ocean wannabeass up!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.25,0:36:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你个狗娘养的 把摄像机关了\NYou shut your fakeass wannabe... Turn these cameras off!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.93,0:36:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 贝基 进来 请坐\NHello, Becky. Come in. Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.03,0:36:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 提安娜\NSo, uh, Tiana...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.87,0:36:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,很不幸的是 因为针对你的主打歌\Nunfortunately, there was a miscommunication
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.71,0:36:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,出现了一些误会\Nin your lead song, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.54,0:36:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们决定延迟发布你的唱片\Nwe're gonna have to postpone the release of your album.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.08,0:36:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 你什么意思 误会\NNo... What do you mean, a miscommunication?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.25,0:36:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 泽维尔告诉我你录了 星光\NWell, Xavier told me that you recorded Starlight...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.38,0:36:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,某种程度上那算是告密\Nwhich that is lightweight snitchin',
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.18,0:36:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们后面再处理这个\Nbut we gonna deal with that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.89,0:36:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有同意用那首歌\NI did not sign off on that song.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.66,0:36:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所以现在我们要让你重回录音棚\NSo now we got to put you back in the studio
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.69,0:36:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,录制 我 那首我想要的歌\Nto record Me, The song I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.36,0:36:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 你跟我撒谎了\NSo... you lied to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.40,0:36:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 我相信那首歌\NNo. I believed in the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.96,0:36:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能和说谎的人一起工作 酷琦\NI can't work with no liars, Cookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.20,0:36:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让她离开我的团队 什么\NI want her off my team. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.53,0:36:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你认真的吗\NAre you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.77,0:36:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我是这里唯一一个为你争取的人\NI'm the only one around here fighting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.24,0:36:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 看看这有什么好结果\NYeah, and look where it got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.80,0:36:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,酷琦 她现在只是在气头上\NT... Cookie, she's just mad right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.74,0:36:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要让我离开她的团队\NPlease don't take me off her team.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.24,0:36:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是你说的 贝基\NYou said it, Becky.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.51,0:37:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得给艺人他们想要的\NWe got to give the artist what they want. Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.58,0:37:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以试试和她谈谈 看能不能改变她的想法\NI can try and talk to her and see if I can change her mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.62,0:37:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 这都是你自己造成的\Nbut... you did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.25,0:37:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你要学会听话\NYou need to learn how to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.26,0:37:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 我以为你喜欢这歌\NWhat happened? I thought you liked the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.39,0:37:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我是喜欢\NI did.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.73,0:37:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不支持我\NSo why didn't you have my back?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.93,0:37:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是生意\NIt's just business.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.31,0:37:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,她在这儿 酷琦\NThere she is. Cookie,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.61,0:37:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你想把介绍给我一个非常好的朋友\NI'd like to introduce you to a good friend of mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.64,0:37:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,格斯 罗德里格斯\NGus Rodriguez.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.81,0:37:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道戴维斯女士吗\NYou know Ms. Davis.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.31,0:37:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 所以\NOh, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.85,0:37:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是这个意思啊 安吉洛\Nit's like this now, huh, Angelo?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.48,0:37:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我来就是为了道歉的 里昂女士\NI'm here to apologize, Ms. Lyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.35,0:37:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,里昂女士 戴维斯已经因为她过分热心的行为\NMs. Lyon, Officer Davis has been reprimanded
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.95,0:37:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,被训斥过了\Nfor her overzealous behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.99,0:37:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,她希望那样足够歉意\NShe hopes that that will be sufficient,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.49,0:37:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,而你不会投诉我们\Nand you won't choose to file a complaint.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.29,0:37:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会\NI'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.93,0:37:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 这怎么样了\NUh, what's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.20,0:37:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,看着像是我们\NIt seems that we got
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.60,0:37:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,得到了一些和你没什么关系的调查相关的\Nsome wrong information about an ongoing investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.77,0:37:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,错误消息\Nthat has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.24,0:38:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你说是谁告诉她来打压我的\NSo who you saying told her to put the squeeze on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.14,0:38:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能说 但是你一直都规规矩矩\NI'm not at liberty to say, but you've been a model offender,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.54,0:38:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我这边觉得没必要扩大对你的限制\Nand my office sees no reason to extend your restrictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.61,0:38:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我和我兄弟在哥伦比亚打球的时候就认识了\NI've known my man here since we balled at Columbia.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.61,0:38:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他说你是好人 所以你在我这里不会有麻烦\NHe says you're good people; you're good with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.78,0:38:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 我在前面等你\NOkay. I'll wait for you out front.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.72,0:38:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 谢谢\NAll right, man, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.95,0:38:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,三个月后再见 奥洛\NI'll see you in three months, Hollo...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.96,0:38:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,里昂小姐\NMs. Lyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.22,0:38:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,给孩子们我的爱 夏琳娜\NGive the kids my love, Sharlene.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.69,0:38:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你帮我费了些麻烦 是吧\NSo you went to a lot of trouble for me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.06,0:38:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到你儿子们今晚\NI saw your boys tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.83,0:38:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,在帝国极度流的情况了\Non Empire XStream, and, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.80,0:38:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我意识到一些关于你和你家庭的事\NI realized something about you and your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.10,0:38:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我确定整个世界都知道了\NYeah, I'm sure the whole world did.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.30,0:38:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我意识到 争斗\NWell, I realized that... fighting
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.67,0:38:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是你们家族的行为方式\Nis your family's way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.41,0:38:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,它像是流淌在你的血液里的\NIt's... it's like it's in your blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.64,0:38:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但你们都有一种概念\NBut somehow, y'all got the idea that I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.05,0:38:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是一个斗士\NI'm not a fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.68,0:38:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我现在不是试着和你们一起去战斗\NLook, I am not trying to fight with you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.02,0:38:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,小女孩 我不是在说\NBaby girl, I'm not talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.02,0:38:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,和你并肩作战的事\Nfighting with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.82,0:38:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说为你而战\NI'm talking about fighting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.82,0:38:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,如果那意味着和卢修斯作对 那好吧\NAnd if that means going up against Lucious, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.73,0:38:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样吧\Nthen so be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.50,0:39:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯哼\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.10,0:39:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你把我一路从布朗斯维尔带出来\NYou got me all the way out in Brownsville.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.00,0:39:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你准备好谈谈这事了\NI hope you're ready to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.24,0:39:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我想谈这事\NYeah, I'm ready to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.77,0:39:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你准备好过联邦证人保护项目下的生活了吗\NYou ready to be about that WITSEC life?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.41,0:39:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦证人保护项目 你昏头了吧\NWITSEC? You must be smoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.91,0:39:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会打算在给我那具尸体后\NYou ain't gonna be walking around in the sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.88,0:39:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,还在光天化日之下到处晃吧\Nafter giving me a body.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.18,0:39:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你没那么疯狂吧 我的老兄\NEven you ain't that crazy, my G.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.58,0:39:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,什么尸体\NWhat body?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.95,0:39:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那具你和卢修斯\NThe one you and Lucious hid
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.55,0:39:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,藏在卡姆登的一块混凝土板下面的\Nin a slab of concrete back in Camden.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.69,0:39:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你在说什么\NI don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.29,0:39:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我的意思\NYou know what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.73,0:39:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我不想和你捉迷藏了 肖恩\NLook, I ain't the one to be playing with, Shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.76,0:39:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我在全方位向里昂家族施压\NI'm squeezing the Lyon family on all sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.63,0:39:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,让酷琦的假释官对她加强监管\NGot Cookie's P.O. To tighten the leash on her, and I can
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.70,0:39:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我也能随时这样对待你\Nturn that same heat on you anytime I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.54,0:39:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那听起来可不像感恩 塔里克\NThat don't sound like gratitude, Tariq.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.04,0:39:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是我还打算\NEspecially when I'm about to make
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.44,0:39:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,早点给你欢庆圣诞节呢\NChristmas come early for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.45,0:39:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那是谁\NWho's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.71,0:39:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,芙蕾达 盖茨\NThat's Freda Gatz.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.08,0:39:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那个在美国音乐奖上射击了贾马尔 里昂的说唱歌手吗\NThe rapper that shot Jamal Lyon at the ASAs?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.79,0:39:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就是她\NExactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.66,0:40:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道她的爸爸是谁吗\NDo you know who her dad was?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.16,0:40:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,记得弗兰克 盖哲思吗 我当然记得弗兰克\NRemember Frank Gathers? Of course I remember Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.13,0:40:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你 卢修斯和酷琦\NYou, Lucious and Cookie,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.63,0:40:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你过去还替他做事呢\Nyou used to run material for him back in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.90,0:40:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,只是对外宣称的\NAllegedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.27,0:40:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,更重要的是 你知道她的爸爸\NMore importantly, you know her father
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.23,0:40:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,曾和卢修斯被一起关在BCC监狱里\Nwas locked up with Lucious at the BCC.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.14,0:40:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 他在那里被杀了\NYou know, he got killed up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.84,0:40:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 我不敢说这是不是一个巧合 或另有隐情\NNow, I can't tell if it was a coincidence or... or what.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.11,0:40:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.01,0:40:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你意思是卢修斯和这事儿有关吗\NSo you saying Lucious had something to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.75,0:40:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 我不是这意思\NNah, that's not what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.45,0:40:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上 我什么也没说\NActually, I ain't saying nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.25,0:40:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是带着我的狗在这附近转悠\NI'm just taking my dog for a walk through the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.66,0:40:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你和肖恩今天见面的意图\NI know what you was up to in that meeting with Shine today.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.83,0:40:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我也没有对你生气\NI ain't mad at you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.00,0:40:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那是个好主意\NIt was a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.57,0:40:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 说到好主意的话\NWell, when it comes to good ideas,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.47,0:40:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我从你那儿学了很多\Nlet's just say I learned from the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.01,0:40:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是很高兴我能帮忙\NNah, I'm just glad I could help.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.35,0:41:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 我可以一直帮忙的\NI could continue being a help, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.05,0:41:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,肖恩需要一个艺人监理部总监\NShine's gonna need an A&R.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.52,0:41:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你\NLook at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.02,0:41:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,试着从这整件事中\NTrying to get something for yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.46,0:41:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,为你自己捞点好处\Nout of this whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.89,0:41:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是说说而已 是的\NI'm just saying. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.53,0:41:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我会考虑这件事的 好么\NI'll think about it, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.30,0:41:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 让我和我的伙伴们讨论一下\NLook, let me talk to my boy for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.77,0:41:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.81,0:41:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,她就待在你的胸口\NI'ma place her right on your chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.81,0:41:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,她太小了 我觉得我会伤着她\NShe's so tiny, I think I'm gonna break her.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.88,0:41:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不会 别担心\NNah, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.18,0:41:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,相信你自己\NJust trust yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.75,0:41:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样\NRight there.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.48,0:41:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,确定她的脑袋是好好放松的\NMake sure her head is nice and relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.72,0:41:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你是正确的 爸爸\NYou were right, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.05,0:41:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.16,0:41:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让你就这样被整\NI wasn't gonna let you get punked like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.53,0:41:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,如果那意味着\NAnd if that means you got to
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.76,0:41:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你要和你的兄弟争斗的话 那么\Ngo to war with your brothers, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.30,0:41:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样吧\Nso be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.93,0:41:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你对贾马尔的看法也是正确的\NYou were right about Jamal, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.37,0:41:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我知道\NYeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.77,0:41:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,所以这意味着\NSo this means I don't have to
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.24,0:41:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我不必和你再争吵了吗\Nplay tugofwar with you no more?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.74,0:41:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不想的\NI wasn't trying to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.34,0:41:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你想给贝拉最好的 对吗\NYou want what's right for Bella, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.91,0:42:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,想要为她创造一个好的世界\NWant to set the world up for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.21,0:42:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我需要再次从音乐上找回我自己\NBut I need to find myself again, musically.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.85,0:42:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在和肖恩的关系太僵了\NBut things are just so tense with Shine right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.38,0:42:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 别担心他 我搞定了\NAh, don't worry about him. I took care of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.59,0:42:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,看看她\NLook at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.06,0:42:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,在你的臂弯里熟睡\NSound asleep in your arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.53,0:42:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这是第一次她没在我怀里哭喊\NIt's the first time she's not screaming in my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.23,0:42:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,知道为什么吗\NKnow why?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.43,0:42:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你的霸气又回来了\NYou got your swagger back.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.20,0:42:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.44,0:42:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们把她放在这里\NLet's put her down over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.77,0:42:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,当你照顾一个婴儿时\NWhen you swaddle a baby,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.44,0:42:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你要把角落折叠好\Nyou want to bend down the top of the corner
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.98,0:42:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,像是摆一个V形\Nlike you're making a nice V.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.74,0:42:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你把她的头顶\NThen you put her head, the top of her head,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.25,0:42:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,放在那里 就是那里 最上面\Nright there, right there, at the top of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.62,0:42:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 你做到了\NOkay. You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.82,0:42:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,她信任你\NShe trusts you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.55,0:42:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 撑着她的脖子\NYeah, support that neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.79,0:42:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我来 噢\NI got you. Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.06,0:42:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 小宝贝\NOh, little baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.49,0:42:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 你做到了\NOh, you got it,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.60,0:42:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你做到了 你做到了\Nyou got it, you got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.00,0:42:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,她很好 很舒服\NShe's good, she's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.60,0:42:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.27,0:42:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们来谈谈你的音乐\NLet's talk about this music of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.34,0:43:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一些想法\NI have some thoughts about
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.57,0:43:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,关于你合作的人选\Nwho you should and shouldn't be working with.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.41,0:43:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 你应该和肖恩一起做一些歌曲\NAnd, yeah, you should do some songs with Shine,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.64,0:43:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但只做一些\Nbut not all of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.85,0:43:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,可能我会给你制作歌曲\NMaybe I'll produce you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.78,0:43:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,把你变成一个超级毁灭者\NTurn you into a destroyer of souls.
